Package: ConstrainMix
Title: Pseudorandomization with Flexible Constraints
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yanan", "Wang", , "ya-nan.wang@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A tool for generating pseudorandomized lists for psycho/neuro-linguistics 
    and behavioral experiments. It allows users to define flexible constraints 
    (e.g., maximum repetition, minimum distance) and weights to optimize trial sequences.
